""" Images - augment - valid tuple (min, max, n) - minibatch """
images = Images(['files/0_100.jpg', 'files/1_100.jpg', 'files/2_100.jpg',
    'files/0_100g.jpg', 'files/3_100.jpg', 'files/1_100.jpg'], [1, 2, 3, 4,
    5, 6], name='foobar')
images.split = 0.5
images.minibatch = 2
images.augment = -45, 45, 2
g = images.minibatch
x = 0
for _ in g:
    x += 1
self.assertEquals(x, 6)
g = images.minibatch
x = 0
for _ in g:
    x += 1
self.assertEquals(x, 3)
g = images.minibatch
x = 0
for _ in g:
    x += 1
self.assertEquals(x, 0)
os.remove('foobar.h5')
